[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "噂の新人アイドルに、\n歌とダンスを教わってみたー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00805",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ということで、なんとなんとなんと！\n私たちのチャンネルに……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00806",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』の皆さんが\n来てくれました！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00807",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "コンコン！　貴殿の心にお邪魔しまする！\nキツネの鬼門にございます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00808",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "絶対一番、ナンバーワン！　ハムスターのヨハナよ。\nネズミじゃないから、覚えておいて",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00809",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ねこじゃらしよりハンマー！　イザナだよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00810",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "三人",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "三人合わせて、『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00813",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "三人合わせて、『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00812",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "不要",
		"romanized_name": "",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "三人合わせて、『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00811",
		"still_path_hash": "0",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "今回は拙者たちに歌とダンスを教わりたいという\nことでありますな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00814",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "そうなんです！　お願いしてもいいですか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00815",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "もちろんだよ！　そしてうちの三人の中で\n歌とダンスが一番上手なのはヨハナ！　ということで！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00816",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "今日は私が先生となって、みんなを指導するわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00817",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "分かりました、先生。\n今日はもう、なんでも先生の言う通りに動くわ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00818",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "普段言うことを聞かないベップが従順。\n先生、毎日来てくれませんか",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00819",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ヨハナさんの迷惑になるからやめてね……？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00820",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "ま、まあ、やる気は十分なようね。では早速、\nダンスの授業に入るわ。まずはこれを見て",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00821",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "わあ……さすが！　やっぱりアイドルってすごいね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00822",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "私も体幹と体力には自信がある。\nけど、こんな動きはできないわ。表現力が違う",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00823",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "今回覚えてもらうのは、この動きよ。\n大丈夫。手取り足取り教えてあげるから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00824",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "皆さんこんにちは！\n『Ｃｕｔｉｅ☆ＡｎｉｍａＬ』でござる！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00825",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "突然ですが、後ろをご覧くだされ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00826",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "森が広がってるね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00827",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "急にこんな所へ連れて来て、何をするつもり？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00828",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "よくぞ聞いてくれました。\n今回は特別企画でありまする。名付けて……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00829",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "食材は現地調達！　サバイバル料理バトルー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00830",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "現地調達……？　まさか、この森で採れるもので\n料理をしろって言ってるのかしら？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00831",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "そのまさかでござる！　ということで、サバイバルに\n詳しい方々がいらっしゃっています。どうぞ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00832",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "こんにちは！　『ＱＥジーンズ』のキューンです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00833",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "自称サバイバルの専門家、ベップよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00834",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "ヤドヴィガ。キノコ・野草図鑑の内容は記憶済み",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00835",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "サバイバルに詳しいかどうかは分からないけど、\n全力でお手伝いさせていただきます！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00836",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ここからの詳細は、企画したアタシから説明するね！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00837",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "イザナの企画！？\nじゃあ、内容知らなかったの私だけじゃない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00838",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "まあまあ。せっかく『ＱＥジーンズ』と\nコラボするなら、こういうのがやりたかったんだもん",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00839",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 35,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ヨハナだって、ワクワクしてるでしょ？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00840",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 36,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "それは……まあ、そうね。ワクワクしてる",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00841",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 37,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "じゃあ問題ないということで……やることは簡単！\n２チームに分かれて、集めた食材で料理を作るよ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00842",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 38,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それで、より美味しいものを作れたほうが勝ち！\nチームはそのままそれぞれのグループでいいよね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00843",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 39,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "それじゃあ早速、食材集め開始ー！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00844",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 40,
		"localized_name": "イザナ",
		"romanized_name": "Izana",
		"model_path_hash": "3787596258689044991",
		"text": "ほら！　魚がそっちに行ったよ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_048_504_00845",
		"still_path_hash": "4716347634718713212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 41,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "了解……そこっ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00846",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 42,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "きゃっ！　ちょっと、水撥ねさせすぎ！\n私にかかったじゃない！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00847",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 43,
		"localized_name": "鬼門",
		"romanized_name": "Kimon",
		"model_path_hash": "4093314950907503731",
		"text": "ご、ごめん……でも、捕まえたでありまする！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_181_504_00848",
		"still_path_hash": "6299303620813546084",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 44,
		"localized_name": "ヨハナ",
		"romanized_name": "Johanna",
		"model_path_hash": "5020305352148956270",
		"text": "本当！？　やるじゃない！\nこれで料理がキノコと野草だけにならなくて済むわ！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_004_504_00849",
		"still_path_hash": "9072463264798612382",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 45,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
		"model_path_hash": "913274709521753211",
		"text": "ひえー、すごいなあ……ダンスの動画から連続で\n撮影してるのに、ぜんぜん疲れてないみたい",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_200_504_00850",
		"still_path_hash": "7374237645965483172",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 46,
		"localized_name": "ヤドヴィガ",
		"romanized_name": "Jadwiga",
		"model_path_hash": "2111970354351478659",
		"text": "アイドルの体力は侮れない……新たな気付き",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_199_504_00851",
		"still_path_hash": "6170794110252514656",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 47,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "私たちも負けてられない。\nさっき猪を見かけたわ。それを捕まえるのはどう？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_504_00852",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 48,
		"localized_name": "キューン",
		"romanized_name": "Quinn",
